
      Please read the steps before start the  Monitoring APP
***************************************************************************

1. Please before run the project make sure Node Js,MongoDB ,Redis installed in your system.

2. please add your mangodb url in config file( for database connection)

3. for Mqtt currently i'm configured "test.mosquitto.org" broker. if Mqtt you have installed in your pc please add host and port in config file.

4. for testing this App use test folder have two js file for sending data via HTTP,MQTT protocols.(for HTTP POST Method)

5. for subscribing real time data used Socket IO.

6. parsed the data and inserted into two collection call rawdata and live data based on defined structure of data